OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA bright start with some
OL,6,Fgood spells of sunshine. Cloud will
OL,7,Ftend to increase throughout the day,
OL,8,Fwith a few showers developing by the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,12,Frain clearing Sunday leaving a dry but
OL,13,Fcooler day. Remaining cooler early
OL,14,Fnext with further showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain, but also some drier
OL,16,Fand sunnier interludes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
